White paper

INTRODUCTION

In this project I intend to use the EmployeeData.csv Dataset in order to determine employee turnover for a buisness. My dataset has 15000 different instances with 10 variables I can use in order to determine the overall turnover rate.

# packages
library(tidyverse)
library(dplyr)
library(ggplot2)

DATASET

Here I cleaned my variable Satisfation_level so that there were no outliers since there seemed to be issues in the dataset. The other values did not possess any outliers (besides time at company as I felt outliers could be permited there)

satis <- EmployeeData$satisfaction_level
data <- subset(EmployeeData, satis > Lower & satis < Upper)
